sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Lynx as Lynx Skill<br/>(/lynx:audit)
    participant Browser as agent-browser MCP
    participant VW as verdict-writer agent
    participant FS as Filesystem<br/>(e2e-evidence/)

    User->>Lynx: /lynx:audit [scope]
    Lynx->>Browser: navigate to screen URL
    Browser->>FS: screenshot step-01-load.png
    Lynx->>Browser: capture a11y tree snapshot
    Browser->>FS: snapshot step-02-a11y.json
    Lynx->>Browser: check console errors
    Browser->>FS: console step-03-errors.txt
    Lynx->>Browser: interact (tap, scroll, form)
    Browser->>FS: screenshot step-04-interaction.png
    Lynx->>FS: write screen-verdict.md (PASS/FAIL per criterion)
    loop next screen
        Lynx->>Browser: navigate to next screen
        Browser->>FS: evidence files for screen N
        Lynx->>FS: screen-N-verdict.md
    end
    Lynx->>VW: all screens complete — synthesize
    VW->>FS: read all screen-*-verdict.md
    VW->>FS: write run-verdict.md
    VW->>User: final PASS / FAIL / CONDITIONAL verdict
